author: Ali Gray
title: Misspelled signs: When the rules of the road go embarrassingly wrong
text: Read more roadside absurdities » We’re all taught from an early age to obey the rules of the motorway and heed all signs and warnings. But when you come across a misspelt road sign it can be somewhat difficult to take it seriously. Did someone actually get paid to paint this? Photo: Rex Features Go. There. Now. Photo: Alamy A purposeful trap for American tourists. Photo: Rex Features Makes you wonder if the lambs wrote the sign… Photo: Getty Would this sign hold up in court? Photo: Rex Features Just as difficult to spell as they are to navigate. Photo: Rex Features But, seriously. How committed are you? Photo: Getty Wait, are they giving away free Rolos? Photo: Alamy Spend more time laughing and less time worrying behind the wheel. With the AA on your side, you're covered when the unpredictable happens. Find out more at theaa.com
